@startuml
title Fintan Case Studies - Full Stack Application Control Flow

actor User
participant "React Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Redux Store" as Redux
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Spring Boot\nApplication" as SpringBoot
participant "Spring Security" as Security
participant "Repository Layer" as Repository
participant "Database" as DB
participant "gRPC Service" as GRPC
participant "Message Queue\n(ZeroMQ)" as MQ
participant "Background Worker" as Worker
participant "New Relic" as Monitor
participant "Elastic Stack" as Logging
participant "AWS CodeDeploy" as Deploy
participant "Facebook OAuth" as OAuth

== User Authentication Flow ==
User -> Frontend: Access Application
Frontend -> SpringBoot: GET /api/auth/status
SpringBoot -> Security: Check Session
alt Session Invalid
    Security -> SpringBoot: Unauthorized
    SpringBoot -> Frontend: 401 Unauthorized
    Frontend -> User: Redirect to Login
    User -> Frontend: Click OAuth Login
    Frontend -> OAuth: Initiate OAuth Flow
    OAuth -> Frontend: Authorization Code
    Frontend -> SpringBoot: POST /api/auth/callback
    SpringBoot -> OAuth: Verify Token
    OAuth -> SpringBoot: User Profile
    SpringBoot -> Security: Create Session
    Security -> SpringBoot: Session Created
    SpringBoot -> Frontend: Authentication Success
else Session Valid
    Security -> SpringBoot: Authorized
    SpringBoot -> Frontend: 200 OK
end

== Data Retrieval Flow ==
User -> Frontend: Request Data
Frontend -> Redux: Dispatch Action
Redux -> Redux: Update State (Loading)
Redux -> Frontend: Trigger Saga
Frontend -> Gateway: GET /api/data
Gateway -> SpringBoot: Forward Request
SpringBoot -> Security: Validate Authorization
Security -> SpringBoot: Authorized
SpringBoot -> Repository: Query Data
Repository -> DB: Execute Query
DB -> Repository: Return Results
Repository -> SpringBoot: Domain Objects
SpringBoot -> Monitor: Log Performance Metrics
SpringBoot -> Logging: Log Request Details
SpringBoot -> Gateway: JSON Response
Gateway -> Frontend: HTTP 200 + Data
Frontend -> Redux: Dispatch Success Action
Redux -> Redux: Update State (Success)
Redux -> Frontend: Notify Components
Frontend -> User: Display Data

== Async Task Processing Flow ==
User -> Frontend: Submit Long-Running Task
Frontend -> SpringBoot: POST /api/tasks
SpringBoot -> Security: Validate Authorization
Security -> SpringBoot: Authorized
SpringBoot -> MQ: Enqueue Task Message
MQ -> SpringBoot: Acknowledgement
SpringBoot -> Frontend: 202 Accepted (Task ID)
Frontend -> User: Show Processing Status

MQ -> Worker: Dequeue Task Message
Worker -> Repository: Process Task Data
Repository -> DB: Update Records
DB -> Repository: Confirmation
Worker -> GRPC: Prepare Push Notification
GRPC -> Frontend: Stream Update (Server Push)
Frontend -> Redux: Update Task Status
Redux -> Frontend: Notify Components
Frontend -> User: Display Completion

== CI/CD Deployment Flow ==
participant "Developer" as Dev
participant "Git Repository" as Git
participant "CircleCI/Azure\nDevOps" as CI
participant "AWS CodeBuild" as Build

Dev -> Git: Push Code Changes
Git -> CI: Trigger Webhook
CI -> CI: Run Tests (UI/Integration)
CI -> Build: Trigger Build
Build -> Build: Execute buildspec.yml
Build -> Build: Build Artifacts
Build -> Deploy: Deploy Artifacts
Deploy -> Deploy: Execute appspec.yml
Deploy -> SpringBoot: Deploy New Version
SpringBoot -> Monitor: Register Deployment
SpringBoot -> Logging: Log Deployment Event
Deploy -> CI: Deployment Success
CI -> Dev: Notification

== Monitoring & Logging Flow ==
SpringBoot -> Monitor: Send APM Metrics
Monitor -> Monitor: Analyze Performance
alt Performance Issue Detected
    Monitor -> Dev: Alert Notification
end

SpringBoot -> Logging: Send Log Events
Logging -> Logging: Index & Aggregate
Logging -> Logging: Analyze Patterns
alt Error Pattern Detected
    Logging -> Dev: Alert Notification
end

== Mobile Application Flow ==
participant "React Native App" as Mobile

User -> Mobile: Open Mobile App
Mobile -> Gateway: GET /api/mobile/data
Gateway -> SpringBoot: Forward Request
SpringBoot -> Security: Validate Token
Security -> SpringBoot: Authorized
SpringBoot -> Repository: Query Data
Repository -> DB: Execute Query
DB -> Repository: Return Results
Repository -> SpringBoot: Domain Objects
SpringBoot -> Gateway: JSON Response
Gateway -> Mobile: HTTP 200 + Data
Mobile -> User: Display Data

Mobile -> GRPC: Subscribe to Updates
GRPC -> Mobile: Stream Notifications
Mobile -> User: Show Push Notification

@enduml
